STEPS TO SEPARATE PROJECT BY FUNCTION 
OUTPUT: JSON FILE WITH ALL FUNCTIONS IN PROJECT 

1. Open Joern console by opening your terminal on the path where the project you want to analyse. 
2. Enter the name of the folder containing the whole project, example for RIOT project: joern> importCode("RIOT-master") 
3. Enter following query -> joern> 
cpg.method.where(_.columnNumber).whereNot(_.name("<global>")).map(m=>(m.name, m.callee.whereNot(_.name("<operator>.*")).l.size,m.start.dump)).toJsonPretty |> "callperfunc_riot.json"  
